title: Blinc Kiss Me Mascara Black
description: Buy Blinc Mascaras - Blinc Kiss Me Mascara Black. How-to-Use: To apply: use the wand applicator and gently sweep the wand across the brow line in short strokes to give the appearance of natural hairs. This will allow you to determine the desired thickness or thinness of the brow. Apply additional coats for deeper color. To remove: at the end of the day, remove with any gentle makeup remover.Tips and tricks: Use on skin, even when no brows are there. Will last until you are ready

title: Neutrogena Deep Clean Shine Control Blotting Sheets, 50 Count (Pack of 2)
description: These silky, ultra-absorbent sheets are softer than paper and are uniquely designed to reduce shine by 95% and instantly remove excess surface oil that may clog pores without overdrying skin or disturbing makeup, controlling shine for up to four hours. Skin is left with a fresh, matte finish. See the oil on the sheet and not on your face. Perfect for touch-ups when you're on the go.
